{"tid":1312241,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日開始見一黑警屌一個 用最令用佢羞恥嘅言語","createTime":"2019-07-13T13:01:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T13:13:12.000Z","uid":63364,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"358869ef00d1cb461bbdf1a98517c1a429e45567","tid":1312241,"uid":63364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:01:15.000Z","msg":"辱警罪講左好耐 只係未放上立法會<br />\n今次運動之後一定會借勢推<br />\n呢一刻屌唔屌佢都會推<br />\n就要將仇警情緒一直保溫<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻嘅政府只淨下警隊去對應我地嘅訴求<br />\n必定要令警隊失效<br />\n必定要打散警隊示氣<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻黑警已經係同警犬一樣，啲腎上腺數谷住谷住<br />\n指揮官只會喺有得打嘅時候先放啲狗出嚟亂咬<br />\n要全面錯佢銳氣<br />\n<br />\n最後，大家小心，切勿阻差辦公"},{"pid":"4f875803e13440f435ec84fd6c2c6adc6282da80","tid":1312241,"uid":63364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:01:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2fac9f08ff7c2938110b4285c3be8e033abe2404","tid":1312241,"uid":63364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:02:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"52f6e2f27481a86e6b00a0968ec6f5ab138f299a","tid":1312241,"uid":63364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:02:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b9443a06a37b8e34e6353d80660fb561f349ef4f","tid":1312241,"uid":63364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:02:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"62c04f2693aeb3af856f629e9a3e839bdb209209","tid":1312241,"uid":63364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:02:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"574433e86b3be63e1b28095bab3af453e28cbb0c","tid":1312241,"uid":63364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:02:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2c878a6def4c8e76fadf7a9b5e9e70554cf7c4ed","tid":1312241,"uid":63364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:02:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"69c7e5450e32dc53b927ec5d1e12256c55c594db","tid":1312241,"uid":63364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:08:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"65cbace789